Designing Human Centered Software Class Assignment

A simple application that displays a target square (in red) and a targetting square (in grey).
The target square has a random X/Y position, as well as a random
rotation and scale (think of it as a Z position).

The goal to create a multi-dimensional input method for
rotating, scaling and translating the target square onto the targeting
square as quickly and accuratly as possible.

That works just fine on phone